title: Las Iguanas
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Mexican, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Latin American inspired chain restaurant in Festival Place shopping centre. Serves South and Central American food and cocktails. Has a separate vegetarian menu where vegan dishes are marked; several vegan mains and desserts. Parking in the nearby shopping centre. Accessible on foot from bus and train stations.
